item.title: TF2 update
item.dc:creator: av3nger
item.description:
Savant:

verify integrity of game cache?

or try deleting C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\YO, YOUR ACC. GOES HERE\team fortress 2 (be sure to backup sounds/skins so you don’t have to download them again)
If all else fails, contact steam support

I don’t think you want a custom model or sounds when you join a pure server, because your custom model will get wire framed, and the sounds will make your ears fuckin bleed.
